f=Product/ux/custom/synthesis-discipline/SKILL.md · in=Turning raw research data claims carry their confidence traceable evidence, never vibes. synthesized finding says what knows, strongly, what; "users seem frustrated" without trace finding. · p=Synthesis good data becomes bad conclusions: researcher's prior gets read three ambiguous quotes shipped certainty. Disciplined synthesis makes claim traceable data honestly weighted, PRDs cite evidence, researcher's hunch. · wu=study-design hands over raw data (interviews, test sessions, survey results)., Voice-of-customer verbatims need pattern extraction., claim about users about enter PRD repository (the confidence gate). · st:/ Protocol=EVIDENCE FIRST (claims built data, data mined pre-held claim confirmation bias enemy) PATTERN (recurring signals across sources, counts; one-person quote hypothesis, finding) CLAIM CONFIDENCE (each claim tagged: strong moderate directional, keyed sample size, consistency, method flag rides claim everywhere it's cited) TRACE (every claim links supporting data quotes, session refs, response counts) DISCONFIRMING (actively note what contradicted claim; synthesis zero counter-evidence suspect) FILE (confidence-flagged claims research-repository, tagged). · in=Build up, don't mine down start what data says, conclusion you expected; expected-answer-found finding distrust most. Counts matter: "several users" number say it. pattern pattern across sources; one vivid quote hypothesis next study. Confidence explicit calibrated: strong (large/consistent/right-method), moderate, directional flag travels claim PRDs repo (spec's Confidence cap reads it). Trace it's vibe: claim carries evidence links; untraceable claim deleted, softened. Seek disconfirming evidence: note what didn't fit; too-clean finding usually means counter-signal ignored (the anti-confirmation-bias rule, house discipline). · of=Synthesis: claim confidence (strong/moderate/directional why) supporting evidence (quotes/counts/refs) disconfirming notes repository entry. · pr=Evidence up, conclusion down distrust expected answer., Confidence calibrated travels claim., Trace delete; note what didn't fit. · f=Data thin any confident claim? "Inconclusive directional signal only, needs more" valid, honest output better manufactured finding (gauge's honest-missing, synthesis edition). · b:with Other Skills=study-design supplies raw data; research-repository stores confidence-flagged claims; spec's evidence-ladder caps Confidence using flags., loom consumes synthesis check whether experiment's assumption held; shipped miss traced over-confident synthesis annealing lesson (this skill's text updates)., Behavioral Science (future) owns bias/persuasion theory; applies anti-bias *method* here, doesn't inline theory.